<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Recuperar Senha - Conecta Eventos</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #2f4054;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .logo img {
      height: 30px;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      margin: 0 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .btn-entrar-top {
      background-color: white;
      color: #2f4054;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .texto-info {
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    .texto-info h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #2f4054;
    }

    .texto-info p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .form-container {
      max-width: 350px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .form-container h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #2f4054;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .form-group input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #2f4054;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .btn-recuperar {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #2f4054;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .voltar {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .voltar a {
      color: #2f4054;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .voltar a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #888;
      padding: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .form-container {
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo Conecta Eventos" />
      <strong>CONECTA EVENTOS</strong>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/eventos">Eventos</a>
      <a href="/criar">Criar Eventos</a>
      <a href="/inscritos">Eventos Inscritos</a>
    </nav>
    <button class="btn-entrar-top">Entrar</button>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <div class="texto-info">
      <h1>Simplifique a Gestão dos seus Eventos</h1>
      <p>
        Crie, atualize e acompanhe eventos com facilidade usando nosso sistema intuitivo.<br/>
        Comece agora a organizar seus eventos com mais eficiência!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="form-container">
      <h2>Recuperação de Senha</h2>
      <form action="/recuperar" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Digite o seu e-mail" required />
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn-recuperar">Enviar email de recuperação</button>
      </form>

      <div class="voltar">
        <a href="/login">Voltar para tela de login</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    Copyright © 2025 | Conecta Eventos
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
